# URL Auto Refresher + Agentic layer

**Product:** Chromium Manifest V3 **Edge extension** — scheduled tab refreshes, optional sync groups, jitter, focus-aware badge. **Plan / epics:** [doc/plan/EDGE_URL_AUTO_REFRESHER_PLAN.md](doc/plan/EDGE_URL_AUTO_REFRESHER_PLAN.md).

Cursor rules, skills, handoff protocol, and test discipline from [AgenticTemplate](https://github.com/pbuckles22/AgenticTemplate). Document your toolchain in AGENT_HANDOFF.md and TEST_PLAN.md.

Source of truth: PM_PLAN.md, AGENT_HANDOFF.md; .cursor/skills/ (DEV_GUIDE, TEST_TDD, DESIGN_SYSTEM, techwriter, tester, code-reviewer, tech-debt-evaluator, pm-governance, ui-ux, visual-match). Use techwriter for docs; use tester + .cursor/rules/testing.mdc for black-box tests. **TDD:** Read TEST_TDD.md and tester skill first; **Tier 1 (Vitest) and Tier 2 (Playwright)** use test-first before production code when that tier applies. **CI gate:** Before considering work merge-ready, run **`npm run ci`** (tests + build + E2E); GitHub Actions enforces the same on push/PR.

